# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# RESEND + SUPABASE AUTH SETUP  (one-time, in Supabase dashboard)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# All DartVoice emails are sent via Resend from the dartvoice.app domain.
# Two channels:
#   1. OTP emails — sent by Supabase Auth using Resend SMTP
#   2. Lifecycle emails — sent by edge functions via Resend API
#
# ─── DOMAIN VERIFICATION (Resend dashboard) ───────────────────────────────
#   1. resend.com → Domains → Add Domain → dartvoice.app
#   2. Add the DNS records Resend gives you (DKIM, SPF, DMARC) to your
#      domain registrar (e.g. Cloudflare, Namecheap, etc.)
#   3. Wait for verification to complete (usually < 5 min)
#
# ─── SUPABASE AUTH SMTP (OTP emails) ─────────────────────────────────────
#   In Supabase dashboard:
#   Authentication → Settings → SMTP Provider → Enable custom SMTP
#     Host:     smtp.resend.com
#     Port:     465
#     Username: resend
#     Password: <your Resend API key>
#     Sender:   DartVoice <noreply@dartvoice.app>
#
# ─── OTP EMAIL TEMPLATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Authentication → Email Templates → Magic Link / OTP
#   Paste the HTML from emails/email-otp.html
#   (Uses {{ .Token }} placeholder for the 6-digit code)
#
# ─── OTP EXPIRY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Authentication → Settings → OTP Expiry: 600 seconds
#
# ─── EDGE FUNCTION SECRETS ───────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Set in Supabase dashboard → Settings → Edge Functions → Secrets:
#     RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxx
#
#   Edge functions that use it:
#     send-dartvoice-email  — generic lifecycle email sender
#     send-confirmation     — triggered by dartvoice_subscriptions changes
#     notify-contact        — contact form notifications
#
# That's it — billing.py calls supabase.auth.sign_in_with_otp()
# and Supabase+Resend handles OTP delivery automatically.
# Lifecycle emails are sent by the edge functions via Resend API.
